snippet: Chase Utley extended his hot start with the tiebreaking homer among three hits, sparking the Philadelphia Phillies to a 4-3 victory over the Miami Marlins on Sunday for a three-game sweep....

headline.print_headline: Utley Has 3 Hits, HR Gives Phils Win Over Marlins
headline.main: Utley Has 3 Hits, HR Gives Phils Win Over Marlins

lead_paragraph: Chase Utley extended his hot start with the tiebreaking homer among three hits, sparking the Philadelphia Phillies to a 4-3 victory over the Miami Marlins on Sunday for a three-game sweep.
